  category xorg/driver
 attribute X11R7 x11 makej
   require xorg-server
   require xkeyboard-config
  optional setxkbmap '' '' to set keyboard using X keyboard extention
  optional xkbcomp   '' '' is a keymap compiler for the XKB keyboard descriptions
  optional xkbevd    '' '' for a XKB event deamon
  optional xkbprint  '' '' to print XKB keyboard descriptions
  optional xkbutils  '' '' for some additional keyboard utilities
    source $XORG_URL driver/xf86-input-keyboard-$VERSION.tar.bz2
